Maxe
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
A small Chip8/Superchip/Chip16 simulator.

About.
---------------------------------------------------------------------------------
This is a small C8/SCHIP/C16 simulator for the libretro platform, created by
Themaister.

It is intended to be highly modular and portable, written in C++.

